<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272159>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Semeloidea (s. l.) bexhavenensis sp. nov. A. Specimen L 4665. Scale bar is 3 mm. A 1. Dorsal view. A 2. Lateral view of left valve. A 3. Anterior view. A 4. Lateral view of right valve. B. Specimen L 4666 (holotype). Scale bar is 3 mm. B 1. Lateral view of right valve. B 2. Dorsal view. B 3. Lateral view of left valve. B 4. Anterior view. C. Shell fragment from anteroventral portion of left valve of specimen L 4666, showing corrugated nature. Scale bar is 1 mm. C 1. Internal surface. C 2. External surface. C 3. View from the shell edge." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

